The '''1969 South Carolina Gamecocks football team''' represented the [[University of South Carolina]] during the [[1969 college football season]]. Led by head coach [[Paul Dietzel]], the Gamecocks won the [[Atlantic Coast Conference|ACC]] championship and were invited to the {{alternate links|1969 Peach Bowl|Chick-fil-A Bowl|title=Peach Bowl}}.
